loader/ - a C++ interface for dlsym/dlopen
progname/ - a cross-platform interface for getting the path of the current executable
other/isnum.c - a simple function for checking if a string is a number
other/printr.h - an extensive set of extensions for C++23 <print>
other/types.h - a set of typedefs to be similar to rusts types
